Template: partman-reiserfs/options
Type: multiselect
__Choices: notail - set this option for the partition containing /boot, noatime - do not update inode access times at each access, nodev - do not support character or block special devices, nosuid - ignore set-user-identifier or set-group-identifier bits, noexec - do not allow execution of any binaries, ro - mount the file system read-only, sync - all input/output activities occur synchronously, usrquota - user disk quota accounting enabled, grpquota - group disk quota accounting enabled
_Description: Mount options:
 Mount options can tune the behavior of the file system.

